# Scraper API Test Requests
# Use with REST Client extension in VSCode or with curl

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiVersion = v1

### Get API Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}

### Test Scraper Service (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/test
Authorization: Bearer <your-token-here>

### Search Businesses on Google Maps (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your-token-here>

{
  "city": "New York",
  "category": "restaurant",
  "limit": 5
}

### Search Businesses on Google Maps - Different City
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your-token-here>

{
  "city": "Los Angeles",
  "category": "technology",
  "limit": 3
}

### Search Businesses on Google Maps - More Results
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your-token-here>

{
  "city": "Chicago",
  "category": "retail",
  "limit": 10
}

### Test Public Endpoint (development only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "San Francisco",
  "category": "cafe",
  "limit": 2
}

### Get Scraper Statistics (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/stats
Authorization: Bearer <your-token-here>

### Test Validation - Missing City
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "restaurant",
  "limit": 5
}

### Test Validation - Missing Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "New York",
  "limit": 5
}

### Test Validation - Invalid Limit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/scraper/maps-search/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "New York",
  "category": "restaurant",
  "limit": -5
}